s from the user-item\nmatrix with high accuracy and effectiveness, and lead to a performance gain\nover the state-of-the-art RS models by an average of 17%.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 May 2022 16:31:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-20"}
