 large-scale power, (ii)\nsignificant contribution from non-Gaussianity in the cosmic variance as\nexpected following Mondal et al. (iii) an over-estimate of the 21-cm PS of\n10-20 per cent following wedge mode excision for our particular model and (iv)\ntiling smaller volume simulations under-estimates the large-scale power and\nalso the estimated cosmic variance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 May 2022 04:45:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-14"}
