bles us to study the highly heterogeneous microstructure and\nmonitor the uncertainty in failure mechanics. Several numerical examples are\ngiven to examine the efficiency of the proposed method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 May 2022 15:54:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-10"}
